summary: Decentralized Freelancers Marketplace for Trust and Security: AutonNET - AutonNET is a decentralized freelancers marketplace that focuses on trust and security. It offers features like user-friendly interface, order tracking, live support, decentralized learning, and more. The platform is powered by a utility token for AI services and incentivizes data sharing for AI training. AutonNET also has a roadmap for short-term goals and plans for global market expansion.
